Package: ky.gov
Title: Kentucky GIS Server API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Kentucky GIS Server ArcGIS REST API. Covers city/municipality boundaries with population data, traffic webcam locations, and National Register landmark listings.
